1; the possibilities are endless!</p>\n<p><a class=\"btn btn-primary\" title=\"Doppelganger Bar\" href=\"http://www.pagelines.com/store/sections/doppelganger-bar/\" target=\"_blank\">Overview</a><a class=\"btn\" title=\"Doppelganger Bar\" href=\"http://evanmattson.pagelines.me/sections/doppelganger-bar/\" target=\"_blank\">Demo</a></p>\n<hr />\n<p><a title=\"View the Social Counter add-on\" href=\"http://www.pagelines.com/store/sections/social-counter/\" target=\"_blank\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-9688\" alt=\"social counter\" src=\"http://www.pagelines.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/social_counter.png\" width=\"644\" height=\"321\" /></a></p>\n<h2>Social Counter</h2>\n<p>The Social Counter section lets you show off your social media street cred like a boss. Display follower numbers for Facebook, Twitter, Dribble, RSS, YouTube, Instagram, and WordPress with multiple layout and color options.</p>\n<p><a class=\"btn btn-primary\" title=\"Social Counter\" href=\"http://www.pagelines.com/store/sections/social-counter/\" target=\"_blank\">Overview</a> <a class=\"btn\" title=\"Social Counter\" href=\"http://adammunns.com/social-counter\" target=\"_blank\">Demo</a></p>\n<hr />\n<p><a title=\"View the Hooker plugin\" href=\"http://www.pagelines.com/store/plugins/hooker/\" target=\"_blank\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-9689\" alt=\"hooker plugin\" src=\"http://www.pagelines.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/hooker_email.png\" width=\"644\" height=\"328\" /></a></p>\n<h2>Hooker</h2>\n<p>Finally.. the tool you have been dreaming about! With this plugin you can add HTML, JavaScript, and PHP <em>anywhere</em> on your website using built-in PageLines Hooks. Just select a hook from the dropdown box, add custom code, and click save. Too easy!</p>\n<p><a class=\"btn btn-primary\" title=\"Hooker\" href=\"http://www.pagelines.com/store/plugins/hooker/\" target=\"_blank\">Overview</a> <a class=\"btn\" title=\"Hooker\" href=\"http://www.pagelines.com/plus/\" target=\"_blank\">Now FREE with Plus</a></p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Have a great idea for a new section or plugin? <a href=\"http://www.pagelines.com/contact/\" title=\"Contact us\" target=\"_blank\">Let us know</a>!</strong></p>\n<div id=\"wpcr_respond_1\"></div><p>The post <a href=\"http://www.pagelines.com/pagelines-store-your-march-update/\">PageLines Store: Your March Update</a> appeared first on <a href=\"http://www.pagelines.com\">PageLines</a>.</p>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:64:\"http://www.pagelines.com/pagelines-store-your-march-update/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"5\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:29:\"http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/\";a:1:{s:7:\"content\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:5:{s:3:\"url\";s:76:\"http://www.pagelines.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/march-update-130x130.png\";s:5:\"width\";s:3:\"130\";s:6:\"height\";s:3:\"130\";s:6:\"medium\";s:5:\"image\";s:4:\"type\";s:9:\"image/png\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:2;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:66:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:6:{s:0:\"\";a:8:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:40:\"Introducing the PageLines Support Center\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:70:\"h