te\" target=\"_blank\">WordCamp San Francisco</a>!  Check out some of the photos taken at the event by <a href=\"http://www.twitter.com/photo\" title=\"@photo\" target=\"_blank\">Michael O&#8217;Donnell</a> &#8211; Great SF area photographer.</p>\n<p>As you can see below,  <a href=\"http://twitter.com/#!/search/%23wcsf\" title=\"wcsf hashtag\" target=\"_blank\">#WCSF</a> was a huge success!  I think the most interesting part about the &#8220;State of the Word&#8221; is the term &#8220;App Engine&#8221; that Matt used during his presentation.  The way <a href=\"http://www.wordpress.org/\" title=\"WordPress.org\" target=\"_blank\">WordPress</a> has evolved from a blog, to a CMS, and now into the future as a platform for developing almost anything is exciting!!\\</p>\n\n<a href=\'http://www.pagelines.com/wordcamp-san-francisco/2012-08-04-11-06-24-2-2/\' title=\'2012-08-04-11-06-24-2\'><img data-attachment-id=\"8784\" data-orig-file=\"http://www.pagelines.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/08/2012-08-04-11-06-24-21.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"2048,1365\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;4&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;Canon EOS 5D Mark III&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1344078384&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;24&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;6400&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0.0333333333333&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"2012-08-04-11-06-24-2\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"http://www.pagelines.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/08/2012-08-04-11-06-24-21-300x200.jpg\" data-large-file=\"http://www.pagelines.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/08/2012-08-04-11-06-24-21-560x373.jpg\" width=\"130\" height=\"130\" src=\"http://www.pagelines.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/08/2012-08-04-11-06-24-21-130x130.jpg\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail\" alt=\"2012-08-04-11-06-24-2\" /></a>\n<a href=\'http://w